description:
This Pack expands your style choices even further to include the Robot and Desert fox, each with their own selection of customisation options!

For each Tray Racers! Supporter's Pack purchased we'll plant a tree with Ecosia.

These trees will be planted across a range of projects, benefitting both people and planet. From restoring desertified land in Burkina Faso to protecting endangered plants and animals in Brazil.
name: Tray Racers! Supporter's Pack
